Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.60,0:01:19.56,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(962,78.381)\blur4}住在初夏的间隙里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.56,0:01:22.19,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(962,78.381)\blur4}那朵高贵之花
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.19,0:01:27.44,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(962,78.381)\blur4}是我传达不到的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.44,0:01:30.24,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(962,78.381)\blur4}藏在言语的深处
