Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.82,0:01:38.08,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(962,78.381)\blur4}早已因为没有阳光沐浴枯萎了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.08,0:01:40.12,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(962,78.381)\blur4}和周围对比后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.12,0:01:43.29,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(962,78.381)\blur4}又陷入自我讨厌中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.29,0:01:45.54,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(962,78.381)\blur4}即使很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:49.38,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(962,78.381)\blur4}但全部都被你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.38,0:01:51.55,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(962,78.381)\blur4}拯救了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.93,0:01:58.31,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(962,78.381)\blur4}是你让我看见
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.31,0:02:03.73,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(962,78.381)\blur4}这世界是多么美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.73,0:02:09.11,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(962,78.381)\blur4}好像我变得不再像是我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.11,0:02:11.40,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(962,78.381)\blur4}就算这样的日子里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.40,0:02:14.20,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(962,78.381)\blur4}也有可爱之处
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.20,0:02:18.20,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(962,78.381)\blur4}还知晓对你的恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.62,0:00:59.62,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}君が僕に見せてくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.62,0:01:05.50,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}世界はとても綺麗だったな
